name: Hentai Senpai: Sukebe Nekomimi no Yoru
name_original: Hentai Senpai: Sukebe Nekomimi no Yoru
description:
Hentai Senpai: Sukebe Nekomimi no Yoru is a FREE puzzle game featuring sexy Nekomimi to play with!

Swapping and Rotating Puzzles

2 classic puzzles to play! Play either puzzle to unlock more Nekomimi to play with!

16 FREE Nekomimi's

16 Nekomimi's to play with for FREE!

High Quality Nekomimi

All Nekomimi is in glorious 4K!

Nekomimi Gallery

Easy to use gallery to see that Nekomimi up close!

Favourites System

Favourite your most loved Nekomimi to get quick access to them!

Chill Music

Chill music to listen to while playing with your Nekomimi!

Technical Settings

All the settings you need, including resolution, fullscreen, framerate cap, vsync and more!
